		<fdd:description>Bitstream encoding and file format designed for efficient distribution of sound files over moderate bandwidth connections; Vorbis encoding may be used at higher data rates for better fidelity.</fdd:description>
		<fdd:shortDescription>Bitstream encoding and file format designed for efficient distribution of sound files over moderate bandwidth connections.</fdd:shortDescription>
